title: Cueto tosses gem as Royals beat Astros 7-2 in ALDS clincher
text:
> Sports Cueto tosses gem as Royals beat Astros 7-2 in ALDS clincher Houston Astros starting pitcher Collin McHugh walks to the dugout after being taken out of the game in the fifth inning of Game 5 in baseball's American League Division Series against the Kansas City Royals, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Kansas City, Mo.
